HEADWORD: Fee-faw-fum
<hw>Fee`-faw`-fum"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A nonsensical
exclamation attributed to giants and ogres; hence, any expression
calculated to impose upon the timid and ignorant.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Impudent
<xex>fee-faw-fums</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>J. H. Newman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Feejee</ent>⟦br⟧
